*Description:
-------------
This is the translation of following mod into Japanese.

Skyrim NEXUS: Hunting in Skyrim - A Hunting Guild(ver 1.3.6)
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/18866/

TES Alliance: Hunting in Skyrim - A Hunting Guild(ver 1.3.5)
http://tesalliance.org/forums/index.php?/files/file/1267-hunting-in-skyrim-a-hunting-guild/

AFK Mods: Hunting in Skyrim - A Hunting Guild(ver 1.3.5)
http://afkmods.iguanadons.net/index.php?/files/file/803-hunting-in-skyrim-a-hunting-guild/


But please be careful for version, This is only for ver 1.3.6.

------------
*how to use:
------------
1.Install Hunting in Skyrim - A Hunting Guild(ver 1.3.6)
2.Overwrite [Hunting in Skyrim.esp] of original esp.
